Package com.skyisland.questmanager.quest.requirements

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArriveRequirement
    Requirement that a participant must arrive at a location (or be within some radius of it) This requirement does not require that a participant stay at the location.
    ArriveRequirement.ArriveFactory  
    ChestRequirement
    Requirement that a participant must interact (right click or left click or both) a certain block.
    ChestRequirement.ChestRequirementFactory  
    CountdownRequirement
    Requires a certain amount of time to pass before satisfied
    CountdownRequirement.CountdownFactory  
    DeliverRequirement
    Requirement specification that checks for an itemstack and removes it when it's there
    DeliverRequirement.DeliverFactory  
    InteractRequirement
    Requirement that a participant must interact (right click or left click or both) a certain block.
    InteractRequirement.InteractFactory  
    PositionRequirement
    Requirement that a participant must be at the provided location.
    PositionRequirement.PositionFactory  
    PossessRequirement
    Requirement specification that requires the user to have some quantity of a specific item This requirement can also check whether or not the name of the item matches one given to it
    PossessRequirement.PossessFactory  
    Requirement
    Represents a specific requirement needed to achieve a goal in a quest.
    RequirementUpdateEvent  
    SlayRequirement
    Requires the participants to defeat (kill) some number of a type of entity.
    SlayRequirement.SlayFactory  
    TalkRequirement
    Requirement that a participant must talk to an npc.
    TalkRequirement.TalkRequirementFactory  
    TimeRequirement
    Requirement that a specific time range be current.
    TimeRequirement.TimeFactory  
    VanquishRequirement
    Requirement that a given entity must be slain.
    VanquishRequirement.VanquishFactory
